data.description: Come check out this Charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home seamlessly blending classic allure with modern comfort. Nestled in a friendly Pasadena neighborhood, this home is perfect for those seeking an inviting space to call their own. All bedrooms are large in size. Large den ample livingroom. Open kitchen overlooking den. Large fenced in backyard. 2 car garage large double driveway. Schedule an exclusive tour today and envision the lifestyle that awaits you in this captivating home.
